import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Accueil from './Pages/Accueil'
import Header from './Components/Header'

function App() {
	return (
			<BrowserRouter>
			<Header />
                <Routes>
					<Route path="/" element={<Accueil />} />
				</Routes>
			</BrowserRouter>
	)
}

export default App
